{"tid":2170061,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"特朗普：美國可以和中國脫鉤，停止業務往來","createTime":"2020-08-23T04:04:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T03:29:52.000Z","uid":48040,"like":211,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"738443fd5a087c3754136b761dbce886e79311aa","tid":2170061,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T04:04:46.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普在周日播出的福克斯新聞採訪中提出，有可能將美國經濟與中國完全脫鉤。<br />\n<br />\n在節目中，特朗普告訴主持Steve Hilton「我們並非必須與中國做生意不可」，然後針對「脫鉤」說：「如果他們不正確對待我們，我肯定會的。一定可以。」<br />\n<br />\n特朗普與中國進行了貿易戰，然後在1月達成了部分第一階段貿易協議。但其後特朗普關閉了第二階段談判的大門，稱他對北京處理武漢病毒的方式不滿意。<br />\n<br />\n6月，美國財政部長Steven Mnuchin表示，如果不允許美國公司在中國經濟中進行公平、平等的競爭，將導致美國和中國經濟脫鉤。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/EagleNews_HK/status/1297381505295978498?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEagleNews_HK%2Fstatus%2F1297381505295978498%3Fs%3D20&d=MZ%2BcikgbnzcLbT%2Fpq7%2BWTLP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=152a084f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FEagleNews_HK%2Fstatus%2F1297381505295978498%3Fs%3D20&h=232eb2f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/EagleNews_HK/status/1297381505295978498?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"f0525fecdf41eff52c4f2b8565c96bcc1a1ca7ad","tid":2170061,"uid":313615,"like":8,"dislike":96,"score":-88,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T04:06:06.000Z","msg":"閉關鎖國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb4b60f9573956e98050935ca015e3df82671a3b","tid":2170061,"uid":228955,"like":15,"dislike":18,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T04:06:32.000Z","msg":"係就快啲啦講咁多嘢"},{"pid":"e324ac2d0ab289458d5d11dabacf6863c875a73e","tid":2170061,"uid":277589,"like":37,"dislike":2,"score":35,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-23T04:07:48.000Z","msg":"步署左4年重造供應鍊就係為呢個原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89e605b278fa6ad3d022931c4cfbea59cf7222a2","tid":2170061,"uid":48040,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTim